responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "33E8875347D8D00CA214BC859B5AF83B", "I have seen his words and prayed before his blood altar. Now I repent! It is he who once was. He who fell in a great clash in the celestial realms. He who is named Du\'Airrem the Prime Harvester. REPENT!")
